# Environment variables for SameOldRoads
#
# PRODUCTION (Vercel): set SERPAPI_KEY in Project Settings -> Environment
# Variables. The /api/reviews Edge Function reads it server-side, so the key
# is never shipped to the browser.
#
# LOCAL: copy this file to .env.local and fill in your value. The serverless
# function only runs under `vercel dev` (plain `npm run dev` skips /api).
# .env.local is gitignored — never commit real keys.

SERPAPI_KEY=your_serpapi_key_here
